V (2493)-Donchenko,A (2569) Drancy 2016 (½-½, 38)}) 10... Nc6 11. Nxc6 (11.
Qe2 Na5 $1 $146 12. Rd1 Nxb3 13. axb3 Nd5 $11) 11... bxc6 12. Qf3 a5 13. Na4 (
13. Qxc6 $6 a4 14. Bc2 Bd7 15. Qb7 a3 $36) 13... Qc7 14. Rd1 Nxa4 15. Bxa4 Bb7
