{How Black should proceed here?} 8... c6 $1 {This sacrifice gives Black more
than enough compensation for the pawn.} 9. dxc6 Nxc6 10. Nf3 Bd7 11. Qd1 Qb6 $1
{Black has a bishop pair and active pieces for the pawn. White is behind in
development.} *

